<bug>
    <id>15222</id>
    <title>New feature  Use facebook as Page  and app. installation</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">Since latest refactoring to be able to use  Facebook as Page _ it s no longer possible to install application after this action.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">When trying to add new application_ FB platform display a warning message  You are using Facebook as XXXXXX.</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.2">To access this page_ you ll need to switch from using Facebook as your page to using Facebook as yourself.</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.3">.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="3">
            <sentence id="3.1">At this step_ all is ok_ but on next step_ after validating  Continue as XXXXX  FB redirect to an invalid url (www.facebook.com/...app_name.../ instead of app.facebook.com/...app_name.../).</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="4">
            <sentence id="4.1">Impact: users are no longer able to install application except if they are able to find right URL by theirself or dont switch to use FB as Page ;-(</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
</bug>
